{
  "stem": "6845.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they bought a lovely home and lived-- we lived in-- lived in it-- lived in it for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Actually, all the-- we lived there all-- all our life, while we were in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was quite changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Life was changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was much more strict there, much more supervised, different kind of [? peer-to-peer, ?] no more lice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the friends-- one could pick them, and you didn't have to worry about those things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as far of the division between the Jews and non-Jews, it was existing and everything, but no-- none of us felt as a disadvantaged person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My grandfather was very much respected in the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- god, I hate to talk so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's like bragging.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My-- I never saw my grandfather work in my-- in my lifetime, so which means from age 11, I ne-- so and before, for sure, he didn't work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So all I remember, he live-- had a beautiful, big desk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had a huge, beautiful pipe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it had a ivory-- a little inlay finishing on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he would sit there and speak very seriously, very respectfully, that we had to behave ourselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it-- it-- it was-- it was a wonderful experience.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It-- it was really-- there was-- there really-- we really knew our limitations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My two brothers didn't have it so easy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think they-- they got some spanking from my father, who otherwise was such a easygoing, because they just didn't have that enthusiasm to excel in the school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They just managed, barely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So it wasn't too much of a joy for my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But generally speaking, the life in Uzhorod was wonderful because, as I said, we had relatives there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
